Invocation Name: manchester united songs
des:
Manchester United Songs will bring the sound of Old Trafford right to you. Sing along to the classic, "United Road" and get fired up for game day. This skill will warm the hearts of any United fan and teach your friends and family the lyric of the Red Devils. Come on United!

Is it game day? Ask Alexa to open Manchester United Songs and then say, "It's game day!" You will appreciate her response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
